OL,6,FOnline has become the most popular
OL,7,Fnews source by a small margin, as TV
OL,8,Fviewership continues to decline,
OL,9,Faccording to an Ofcom news consumption
OL,10,Fsurvey.
OL,12,FIts report, which saw market research
OL,13,Fcompany Jigsaw Research conduct 5,466
OL,14,Finterviews, found that 71% view news
OL,15,Fonline, compared to 70% viewing news
OL,16,Fon television.
