OL,9,Fuse online platforms.
OL,11,FYih-Choung Teh, Ofcom group director,
OL,12,Fstrategy and research, said:
OL,13,F"Television has dominated people's
OL,14,Fnews habits since the 1960s, and it
OL,15,Fstill commands really high trust.
OL,17,F"But we're witnessing a generational
OL,18,Fshift to online news, which is often
OL,19,Fseen as less reliable ` together with
OL,20,Fgrowing fears about misinformation and
OL,21,Fdeepfake content."
